ITV.Tour.de.France.2014.Stage.12.Live.PDTV.x264-NX

Thursday 17th July 2014 ITV4
2pm to 5pm Live

Stage 12 is 185km between Bourg-en-Bresse to the Beaujolais hills in Saint-Etienne. A rare day with a flat finale with a lot of pressure on the teams of the sprinters to control the race and not let a breakaway steal the show. Expect a thrilling chase and a blisteringly fast finish. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary by Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting the reporter at the roadside.
